Description: MurOS firewall appliance (backend + UI)
 Simple opensource firewall appliance based on Debian 13.
 Includes stateful nftables filtering, NAT, static routing, VPN
 (WireGuard + strongSwan), HA via keepalived + conntrackd, audit logs,
 SNMP, mail and webhook notifications, all exposed via a web UI.
 .
 This package ships the FastAPI backend, the built React frontend, the
 systemd units and the boot integration. The web UI is reachable on
 https://<host>/ once installed.
